OL,3,CPolice appeal after suspected arson in
OL,4,CYateley Common
OL,6,FPolice are appealing for witnesses
OL,7,Fafter three fires were started on
OL,8,FYateley Common, leaving a large area
OL,9,Fof heathland destroyed and wildlife
OL,10,Fdead.
OL,12,FOfficers were called at around 19:30
OL,13,Fon Friday 3 April to reports of three
OL,14,Fseparate fires between Cricket Hill
OL,15,FLane and Tudor Drive.
OL,17,FHampshire and Isle of Wight Fire and
OL,18,FRescue Service attended and
OL,19,Fextinguished the flames. No injuries
OL,20,Fwere reported.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
