OL,3,CPolice appeal after suspected arson in
OL,4,CYateley Common
OL,6,FAround one hectare of heathland has
OL,7,Fbeen left blackened and burnt.
OL,8,FHampshire County Council said several
OL,9,Freptiles and a small shrew were found
OL,10,Fdead following the blaze, and it is
OL,11,Ffeared many more animals may have been
OL,12,Faffected.
OL,14,FHampshire Police believe a small group
OL,15,Fof children were in the area at the
OL,16,Ftime and is urging anyone who
OL,17,Fwitnessed suspicious behaviour to come
OL,18,Fforward.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
